    <item>
      <title>比亚迪在日本推出第三款电动汽车，但销量仍未起色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/byd-releases-third-ev-in-japan-as-sales-struggle-to-take-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国比亚迪公司在日本推出了其第三款电动汽车，试图在由混合动力汽车和国产品牌主导的市场中找到发展空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/byd-releases-third-ev-in-japan-as-sales-struggle-to-take-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
